data.description: Welcome home to this wonderful 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home on a corner lot. The open floor concept is ideal for entertaining and gatherings. The home has stainless steel appliances, gutters added, complete sprinkler system, 3 inch blinds in the back, custom fit plantation shutters in the front, and a covered back patio. This home is a MUST see.
